title: Captured Essence of LA and Relationship Struggles
review: I really felt for Elliot. Just couldn't get it together romantically or career wise. Loved the location shots too. Very real LA.

title: True to life
review: Relationships are complicated. Brings to focus the all to common oddity of how two people can share such close quarters yet are miles apart.

title: Yes to California No
review: Witty with a solid dose of sarcasm. I can see why it won so many awards.
